      • getCustomObj

        java.lang.Object getCustomObj()
        Returns the transient Custom Object. Does not take part in the KonaKart APIs.
        Returns:
        Returns the customObj object. Note that this is a transient object. It does not get serialised or written to the database and is not read or returned by the KonaKart APIs.

      • setCustomObj

        void setCustomObj(java.lang.Object customObj)
        Set the transient Custom Object. Does not take part in the KonaKart APIs.
        Parameters:
        customObj - Sets the customObj object. This is a transient object. It does not get serialised or written to the database and is not read or returned by the KonaKart APIs.
